<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Lal pien hun kipahum I tung kit tau.
 Lawp tak leh kipakin la saitiu;
 Thihna thim nuoia chute di'n vakna lopi a tung tai,
 Halleluijah lawpin la sa tiu,

[V2]
 A sakmin-Mak, Lemguotthiem Lalpa,
 Kumsawt Pa, Cham Lal lopi ahi;
 A gamin beih tik ni nei puon tin,
 Lien deuh deuh ina kumsawt chanin.

[V3]
 2. Vangkhaw minthang Bethlehem lam zuonin;
 Ginnan chung kawlva bang valeng leng;
 Chun lieng Mari pawm sietlei thangvan Lal liengvai va muitiu
 I neih gothil cheng cheng va piei tiu

[V4]
 3. Ginna'n ka galdawt chung thangvan vangkhuo.
 Chamna Lal mimbang a pienni chun;
 Thangvan mite thakna zaila gihawih chun nuoi simlei leh.
 Ka chung thangvan sang khu a thawng hi.

[V5]
 4. Henkawl ei sut ding Lalthak hung pieng chu.
 A min Lal Krista, Immanuel;
 Hossana!chungnungpen akhun lopi takin um hen la,
 Chamna thu leng hen, nuoi simlei ah.</lyrics>
<title>Lemguot Thiem Lalpa</title>
<hymn_number>13</hymn_number>
<author>Ralngam</author>
</song>